&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fuel the GTM Engine: Collaborate with marketing and the Microsoft Partner Leader to execute joint campaigns, webinars, and events that generate new pipeline and increase Gong&#39;s visibility within the Microsoft ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the Go-To Expert: Act as the internal champion and subject matter expert for all things Microsoft co-sell. You&#39;ll create documentation, run trainings, and provide hands-on support to Gong’s Account Executives on how to best leverage Microsoft programs and funding to win deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operationalize Co-Sell: Be the central point of contact for the Microsoft Partner Center. You&#39;ll manage the submission, tracking, and reporting of co-sell opportunities, working to remove friction and accelerate joint deals with the Microsoft field sales team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track Our Success: Meticulously track and report on all partnership KPIs, including marketplace revenue, co-sell pipeline, and program ROI. You will deliver regular insights to leadership and key stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master the Marketplace: Own the day-to-day management of our Microsoft Marketplace presence, including private offer creation, deal registration, and listing updates, to ensure a seamless and efficient transaction process for our customers and sales team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;QUALIFICATIONS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience including time in a relevant role such as alliances, channel sales, or partner operations within a high-growth B2B SaaS company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct, hands-on experience with the Microsoft Marketplace and Co-sell program is a significant plus and will set you apart.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A master of execution with an &quot;Act Now&quot; mentality. You have a proven track record of being proactive, managing projects flawlessly, and cutting through ambiguity to get things done without waiting for direction.&lt;/li&gt;
